<a:bar xmlns:a="http://ajax.org/2005/aml" class="platform">
    <a:bar id="aisleprefs" class="container" style="
    overflow-y: auto;
    overflow-x: hidden;
    position: absolute;
    left: 0px;
    top: 0px;
    right: 0px;
    bottom: 0px;
    padding-bottom: 130px;">
        <div class="basic intro">
            <h1>Aisle</h1>
            <p>Set up your locale, l10n repos, <code>l10n.ini</code> paths, etc.</p>
            <p style="white-space: normal">For projects like Firefox, use <code>compare-locales</code>.
            Select the basedirectory where your locale is checked out.
            Then select the <code>l10n.ini</code> file to use, something
            like <code>/mozilla-aurora/browser/locales/l10n.ini</code>.</p>
            <p>Add a new project:</p>
            <a:hbox height="40">
                <a:button id="btnAddCompareLocales"
                    style="line-height: 22px" height="24" margin="-2 5 -2 0"
                    skin="blackbutton">compare-locales</a:button>
                <a:button id="btnAddCompareDirs" disabled="true"
                    style="line-height: 22px" height="24" margin="-2 0 -2 0"
                    skin="blackbutton">compare-dirs</a:button>
            </a:hbox>
        </div>
        <a:hbox height="40">
            <a:label width="100">Locale code</a:label>
            <a:textbox class="locale" width="200" initial-message="ab-CD" skin='texbox'/>
        </a:hbox>
        <a:divider skin="c9-divider-hor" margin="5 0 5 0" />
    </a:bar>
</a:bar>
